   <description>All color swatches should be the same size (regardless of # of swatches).  
Each color swatch has a default/unselected-state and active-state
unselected state: no stroke around swatch
selected:
gold stroke around swatch 
color name renders under color swatch
Only one color swatch can be active at a time
Color swatches will enter a carousel when the number of swatches exceeds the breakpoints defined limit
Mobile limit: 5
Desktop limit: 8
When carousel is enabled:
Tap/Clickable arrows will appear
Mobile carrousel will be swipe-able
and if color-swatch name has a disclaimer
then the disclaimer icon will appear as defined through the CMS
when a user clicks on the icon, the disclaimer tooltip will appear in proximity to the asterisk </description>
